# 2008-01-08.jdd.2: Adding Paysimple as a payment provider

### Whereas

1. SPI wishes to provide as much versatility when processing donations as
possible.

2. SPI wishes to decrease overhead in the management of donations.

3. SPI wishes to decrease overall costs in receiving donations.

### The SPI board resolves that

1. SPI shall apply for a financial services account with Paysimple.

2. Upon approval of the application SPI shall add Paysimple as an additional
provider for financial services.

